                    <title>Next Up For AI Chatbots: It’s All About The APIs</title>
                <?php include_once 'Elemental/header.php'; ?><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><br><br><h5> This article is reformatted from originally published at <a href="https://kantrowitz.medium.com/next-up-for-ai-chatbots-its-all-about-the-apis-4df360b22c21"><strong>TDS(Towards Data Science)</strong></a></h5></br><h5> <a href="https://medium.com/?source=post_page-----4df360b22c21--------------------------------">Author : Alex Kantrowitz</a> </h5></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content4 cid-tt5SM2WLsM" id="content4-2" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="row justify-content-center">
                    <div class="title col-md-12 col-lg-9">
                        <h3 class="mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style mb-4 display-2">
                            <strong>Next Up For AI Chatbots: It’s All About The APIs</h3></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">The magical demos displayed the capability. Now the platform wars begin.</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="image3 cid-tt612oXwA9" id="image3-5" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
